body:
Ok, there are many transient errors in Travis build that are related to running the tests inside Docker containers. We're still try to get a handle on that.

For this specific PR, it seems the problem for some tests is the advertised address goes back to `hostname`. I think the fix should be:

``` java
/// Everywhere we bind on localhost
conf.setBindAddress("localhost");

/// Advertise localhost
conf.setAdvertisedAddress("localhost");
```
